{
  "id": "adv_event_2211_01_02",
  "title": "今夜だけは\n仲良しⅢX",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "franさんに「緊急事態！」と言われて来たんですが\n一体、何があったんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san told me \"emergency situation!\" and called me here.\nWhat on earth happened!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.4961677551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "今すぐ宿を変えて下さい！！\nこんな所で一晩を過ごすなんて絶対無理！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Change the inn right now!!\nSpending the night in a place like this is absolutely impossible!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7,
      "endTime": 11.7010655404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "fran、貴方何考えてるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fran‚ what are you thinking?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "endTime": 14.764013671899999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "幽霊がいたなんて理由で、わざわざ\n{user}さんを呼びつけるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calling {user} here just because of a ghost\nis not a reasonable thing to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9666666667,
      "endTime": 19.1634013812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "これも仕事ですから……いや、幽霊が出たと聞いたんで\n一応、応援も連れて来たんですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ this is also part of the job…\nI mean‚ I heard there was a ghost.\nSo I brought some support just in case.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3666666667,
      "endTime": 25.8021995227,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6700.000000000003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あのね、実は芽衣、幽霊が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You see‚ actually‚ Mei loves the occult and ghosts…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8,
      "endTime": 31.055124807400002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "じ、実は芽衣はオカルトとか幽霊が大好きなんですよ！\nだから今回みたいな件には適任と思いましてですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ actually‚ Mei is really into the occult and ghosts!\nSo I thought she would be suitable for a situation like this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2,
      "endTime": 38.8826532365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "私は、たまたま事務所にいたら\n{user}君が「温泉に行きませんか」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I happened to be at the office‚\nand {user}-kun asked‚ \"Do you want to go to a hot spring?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.0666666667,
      "endTime": 46.0746487299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "……まさかそれが幽霊旅館だったなんてね、あはは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I never expected it to be a haunted inn‚ hahaha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2666666667,
      "endTime": 51.3260088603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "あ～、アホくさ\nみんなして幽霊がどうとか騒いでさ、バカじゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ this is so dumb.\nEveryone is making a fuss about ghosts and stuff‚ it's ridiculous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5333333333,
      "endTime": 57.958299478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私は本当に見たんだって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I'm saying I really saw it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1666666667,
      "endTime": 61.7037868182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "と……とにかく、今から宿を変えるのは難しいので\n原因が分かればfranさんも安心して休めますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-anyway‚ it's difficult to change the inn now‚\nbut if we find out the cause‚ fran-san can rest easy‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9,
      "endTime": 68.989999962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "う……それなら、まぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… in that case…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2,
      "endTime": 73.9650793076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、みんなで頑張ろー！\n頑張って調べれば、きっと怖い原因も分かるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ let's do our best together!\nIf we investigate‚ we'll surely find out the scary cause too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1666666667,
      "endTime": 80.156417338,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――温泉旅館を調べる一行",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The group examining a hot spring ryokan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1666666667,
      "endTime": 82.82666666669999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1833.3333333000041
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……\nまさか、本番前日にこんなことになるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh…\nI can't believe this is happening on\nthe day before the performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8666666667,
      "endTime": 90.6741043726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "おかしな足音に、奇妙な人影……\n古い建物だし、変な音がしても不思議ではないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Strange footsteps‚ bizarre figures…\nIt's an old building‚ so weird noises are not surprising‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8666666667,
      "endTime": 98.9614059129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "なんで、それをkanaが調べないといけないんだか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do I have to investigate that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2666666667,
      "endTime": 102.6393876712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に歩き回るより、手分けして調べた方が早いわね\n私は上の階を見てくるわ。貴方達は下から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's faster to split up and search than to walk around together.\nI'll check the upper floors. You all check from below…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9,
      "endTime": 111.1176645279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、そう言ってあんただけサボる気でしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ you're just trying to slack off by saying that‚ aren't you!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.4,
      "endTime": 115.11222214700001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "な～んだ、さんざん偉そうなこと言って\nあなただって、実は怖いんじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ come on‚ you've been talking so big‚\nbut maybe you're actually scared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3666666667,
      "endTime": 122.396507899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "は！？　kanaがビビってる訳ないじゃん\nあんたの目、今度こそバカになったんじゃない！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? Like I'd be scared!\nAre your eyes playing tricks on you this time!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.6,
      "endTime": 128.98832216280002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
